[size=18pt][b]~ BUGFIX ~[/b][/size]

[b]Bug:[/b] When the player is crossing an object he can get stuck.
[b]Example:[/b] When the player is crossing a log and clicks in the middle of the log, the player will be stuck on that spot.

[b]Fix:[/b]
  1. Open the file where your packets are located, in a normal delta this is the client class.
  2. Search for packet 98 which is the forced walking packet.
  Search: 
  [code=java]case 98:[/code]

  3. Add this to the packet:
  [code=java]			if (c.getAgilityHandler().isPassing) {
				return;
			}[/code]

  4. Save and compile, bug fixed. If you find other bugs please let me know.




